#### :pencil2: Exercise 2 {.unnumbered}

Add the following two new variables to data frame `df`

+---------------------------+---------------+
| Variable                  | Coding        |
+===========================+===============+
| SDC_age_category          | \<2 months\   |
|                           | 2-11 months\  |
|                           | 12-23 months\ |
|                           | 24-35 months\ |
|                           | 36-47 months\ |
|                           | 48-59 months  |
+---------------------------+---------------+
| CLIN_fever_onset_category | \<2 days\     |
|                           | 2-3 days\     |
|                           | 4-6 days\     |
|                           | ≥ 7 days      |
+---------------------------+---------------+

